
E-commerce Application

Test Scenarios to Automate

1) Fill the form details and verify Toast error messages displayed appropriately for wrong inputs

2) Shop the items in the app by scrolling to specific Product and add to the into the cart

3) Validate if the items selected in  the page 2 are matching with items displayed in the check out page

4) Validate the total Amount displayed in the checkout pages matches with sum of product amounts selected for Shopping

5) Validate Mobile gestures working for links (long Press) and navigate to WebView

6) Verify if the user can do operations on Web view and can navigate back to the Native App if needed